696
00:41:54,780 --> 00:41:55,700
Nothing.

697
00:41:56,300 --> 00:41:58,420
I just think he's trying to balance

698
00:41:58,420 --> 00:42:00,460
his mother's dignity and his filial duty.

699
00:42:00,460 --> 00:42:01,940
I feel a bit sorry for him.

700
00:42:02,180 --> 00:42:04,060
Go tell him

701
00:42:04,140 --> 00:42:05,260
to come home later.

702
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:06,380
I'm not afraid of chills.

703
00:42:08,140 --> 00:42:08,980
Greetings, My Lady.

704
00:42:09,700 --> 00:42:11,500
