722
00:42:43,820 --> 00:42:45,860
She asks you to come, My Lady.

723
00:42:47,340 --> 00:42:48,940
I should visit Mother.

724
00:42:53,460 --> 00:42:54,620
Chuyu's been

725
00:42:54,620 --> 00:42:56,220
by my side all these years.

726
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:57,860
Now that I'm sending her away,

727
00:42:57,860 --> 00:42:59,540
it should be done with dignity.

728
00:42:59,580 --> 00:43:01,540
If you hadn't tattled,

729
00:43:01,940 --> 00:43:03,220
