739
00:43:20,180 --> 00:43:21,420
I shall take my leave.

740
00:43:22,020 --> 00:43:22,860
Stop right there!

741
00:43:23,460 --> 00:43:24,660
Did I say you could leave?

742
00:43:24,820 --> 00:43:26,420
