749
00:43:41,620 --> 00:43:42,460
Insolence!

750
00:43:42,780 --> 00:43:44,500
How dare you talk back?

751
00:43:44,700 --> 00:43:46,220
Of course you're the enemy's daughter.

752
00:43:46,300 --> 00:43:47,780
You don't even come close to my Chuyu.

753
00:43:49,060 --> 00:43:49,900
True.

754
00:43:50,460 --> 00:43:53,020
You've always wanted Zheng Shu
to marry His Lordship.

755
00:43:53,420 --> 00:43:55,340
Despite all his refusals,

756
00:43:55,460 --> 00:43:57,220
